content: Incredible app realy appreciate this app come to life love it
Love this app so much. Its hard to here what they are saying but, when i can here a voice its nice and clear. Nice job .

The application is built well works as expected however recently my anti-virus picked up on a code change within the app and called for a uninstall as was a TRJN.EXE change applied to the coding I don't know If Brian is aware of this. his apps never throw up warnings as savire as that first time in fact code ran like this (code change, malware detected TRJN.EXE is in coding uninstall now to save device. I use AVG bought and paid for so it keeps my phone on top of things just odd to see that.
